Yeah, how can you ask

23
00:01:32,590 --> 00:01:35,090
a question like that
at a time like this?

24
00:01:35,090 --> 00:01:36,730
Time like what?

25
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:38,220
(groan impatiently)

26
00:01:38,220 --> 00:01:41,980
(sobbing)

27
00:01:45,180 --> 00:01:49,270
