this display of sentiment.

28
00:01:49,270 --> 00:01:52,070
It is just a story, after all.

29
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:54,150
Wind Whistler, it's too bad
you weren't around

30
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:57,950
when the Feelings Fairy
was passing out feelings.

31
00:01:57,940 --> 00:01:59,860
(laughs)

32
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:01,330
I do have feelings..

33
00:02:01,330 --> 00:02:03,950
Which I think
you two just proved.

34
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:07,370
Yeah, by hurting 'em.

35
00:02:07,370 --> 00:02:09,450
Way to go, Buttons.

36
00:02:09,460 --> 00:02:10,710
Moi?

37
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:11,930
(laugh)

38
00:02:18,770 --> 00:02:20,110
Look out!

39
00:02:20,100 --> 00:02:21,960
Crunch the Rockdog comin'!

40
00:02:21,970 --> 00:02:24,230
Run for your lives!

41
00:02:24,220 --> 00:02:28,020
Yeah, run for your lives!
Run! Yeah, run, run!

42
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:32,400
Ow! I'm sorry! No, I'm sorry!

43
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,650
It's okay!
I'm glad you're sorry.

44
00:02:33,650 --> 00:02:35,460
Let's go left!

45
00:02:35,450 --> 00:02:37,610
Right, left! Yeah, right left!
Right left!

46
00:02:37,620 --> 00:02:38,880
That's it, take it to the left!

47
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:40,120
Right!

